	<div class="postzoom"><h1><a href="2007_07_22_reason_why_i_am_writing">Reason why I am writing</a></h1>
<p>As I was looking through some references, I came across the following diagram, from <a href="http://www.lacim.uqam.ca/~chateau/fichiers/stagemaitrise.ps">Practical Public Key Crytposystems</a>:</p>

<p><img src="http://www.caswenson.com/wp-content/uploads/2007/07/bad-diagram.png" alt="Bad Diagram" /></p>

<p>Diagrams like this make me cry.  I hope none of mine look this bad.</p>
